                    </div>
                    <div class="text-align">
                      <h1 class="vermietung-mobile desktop-hide-inline">anbieten</h1>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="heading-list mobile-hidden">
                        <li>Biete Gegenstände an, die du kaum oder nicht mehr verwendest</li>
                        <li>Nutze unsere unverbindliche <a href="#" data-target="#testandbuy" data-toggle="modal"><span class="text-yellow">Test &amp; Buy Option</span></a> </li>
                        <li>Verdiene etwas Geld dabei</li>
                        <li>Lerne neue Menschen kennen</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#reg-modal" class="button-black backgound-yellow text-black mobile-hidden">Jetzt kostenlos mitmachen!</a>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="main-categories main-offers vermietung">
    <div class="container  background-white rent-container bg-white">
        <nav class="crumbs">
            <ul class="col-xs-8">
                <li><a href="{{ path('start-page') }}">hey! VIENNA</a></li>
                <li><a href="{{ path('rental') }}">Equipment vermieten</a></li>
                <li><a class="active-crumb" href="{{ path("rental-detail", { 'categoryId': category.id }) }}">{{ category.name }}</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        {# todo: ? div below doesn't show up anywhere #}
        <div class="mobile-hidden"> <select class="mobile-menu-select desktop-hide" name="forma" onchange="location = this.options[this.selectedIndex].value;">
